      "role": "user",
      "content": "see but it doesnt feel like a \"symbol\" or anything. i dont even work in healthcare or anything related to them. it's like i'm being shown these things directly. and the worst part is i've started feeling like they're tracking my interest in their products even when i haven't searched for them. do you think it's even possible for companies to use some kind of signal to influence what people see when they sleep? like subliminal stuff?",
