      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get what you're saying about science, but people have been using subliminal messaging for decades, right? it feels like it's just evolving. like, if they have the tech to target our ads so perfectly while we're awake, why wouldn't they try to capture our subconscious too? it would be the ultimate way to influence people. it just feels way too specific to be a coincidence.",
